{"tid":1042710,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次見人係香港地鐵咁玩法","createTime":"2019-03-01T17:33:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-02T11:44:40.000Z","uid":20929,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"2b9966a093dd897711258b910e0be2089d3afef6","tid":1042710,"uid":20929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T17:33:05.000Z","msg":"喺youtube簡唔中會睇到啲片內容係喺外國嘅地鐵到做各式各樣嘅嘢，<br />\n可能係跳舞、可能係唱歌，<br />\n咁啱，就係剛才00:10-00:15左右就俾我見到幾個年輕人<br />\n係港鐵到玩雜耍同滑滑板<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲好有氣氛咁播埋上海灘做bgm<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地仲係咁話唔想上高登㖭<br />\n我就覺得咁厲害嘅畫面唔應該淨係得喺地鐵個幾個人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以就想俾大家一齊開心下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過講明先條片極低清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為focuse 咗係第二到，咁多位大佬唔好意思<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/QOYfHOm6J4A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FQOYfHOm6J4A&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7C5gFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=8b93f9fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/QOYfHOm6J4A</a>"},{"pid":"634331a3280996fa9fe774ac37b241fa59ce0b9c","tid":1042710,"uid":16961,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T17:33:49.000Z","msg":"iPhone XS Max 低清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0640f54a29d076af5f97da7a6e0aaa26d3c7e38","tid":1042710,"uid":155815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T17:36:02.000Z","msg":"條片你拍到十年前水準 犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8d5c5622bce3a2fe02aeddc58f9223e07afb09a","tid":1042710,"uid":20929,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"a0640f54a29d076af5f97da7a6e0aaa26d3c7e38","tid":1042710,"uid":155815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T17:36:02.000Z","msg":"條片你拍到十年前水準 犀利<img src=\"